title: Loop 13 CD08 (double disc) 2001
description:
Loop 13 CD08 (double disk limited issue) 2001

A cross section of progressive New Zealand sounds and a reflection of 'The Wave' - The most energized and inspirational era in Aotearoa's audio culture to date.  An era of creative evolution, which has seen a fresh sound emerge.  A sound focused on fun, vision and change.  The pied pipers of the globe...
